translation.Name: Buak_Note_01
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0:
I took the money... I always took the money, always take the money.
I let them get away with murdering their own son, he was so young.- Why, why, why! How can they act like nothing happened, what’s wrong with them!? What’s wrong with me! To get tricked like that, I’m supposed to be better than this! Why, why, why!
